data.title: Nvidia CEO Jensen Huang talks chip restrictions with Trump, blasts state-by-state AI regulations
data.description: Nvidia CEO Jensen Huang told reporters on Capitol Hill that he had just met with President Trump, and the two "talked in general about export controls."
data.author: Annie Palmer
